waka huia
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a receptacle for, originally huia, feathers.
Origin:Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka waka-huia, wakahuia
